y.\n\n\u201cDoesn\u2019t wealthy people have to maintain social distance onboard?\u201d he queried, further asking, \u201cWhy has the government brought such a discriminatory rule for common people?\n\nHe warned that if the aircraft and vehicles are not treated equally, transport entrepreneurs will operate the public transport fully-occupied.","title":"Transport entrepreneurs warn of operating vehicles with fully-occupied seats - Khabarhub","url":"http://english.khabarhub.com/2020/20/128998/","video":[]}
